# 🎯 Number Guessing Game — Modern Web Game

A modern and interactive Number Guessing Game built using HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript with beautiful UI, sound effects, difficulty levels, timer system, and score tracking.

---

# 🚀 Features

## 🎮 Gameplay Features

- 🎯 Multiple Difficulty Levels
- ⏱️ Countdown Timer
- 🏆 High Score System
- 🔊 Sound Effects
- 📊 Live Score Tracking
- 🔁 Multi-Round Gameplay
- 💾 localStorage High Score Saving
- 🎨 Animated Feedback System
- 📱 Responsive Design

